the most of today.

48:11.920 --> 48:14.571
This is even bigger
than Hobby-Con.

48:24.120 --> 48:26.726
Wow. Now,
that's a car.

48:26.920 --> 48:29.526
Whoa. Shiny.

48:56.840 --> 48:57.841
Gagné.

49:11.200 --> 49:12.531
Whoa!

49:21.040 --> 49:23.122
