I have astigmatism and stuff.

50:36.480 --> 50:38.479
Yeah, yeah.

50:43.000 --> 50:44.439
Guy, how do you do it,

50:44.440 --> 50:46.959
shattering your own
records year after year?

50:46.960 --> 50:50.681
Well, when a cheetah
chases after a gazelle,

50:50.840 --> 50:54.208
does he ever stop to think, "Maybe
I've caught enough gazelles.

50:54.400 --> 50:57.324
"Maybe I should just settle
down, try the vegan thing."

50:57.480 --> 51:00.723
No! He keeps running as long
as his legs will carry him.

51:00.880 --> 51:04.407
I am like the cheetah.
I never give up.

51:04.560 --> 51:06.559
Next question.

51:08.200 --> 51:12.000
All right, give me the keys.
I'll drive the first shift home.

51:12.640 --> 51:13.926
Whoa!
What gives?

51:19.480 --> 51:20.720
No, no, no!

51:23.960 --> 51:25.883
Can I help you, monsieur?

51:26.560 --> 51:28.244
One second, please.

51:28.400 --> 51:30.641
What are you doing? Are you
trying to get me arrested?

51:35.400 --> 51:36.479
Oh.

51:36.480 --> 51:39.768
Sorry! So sorry. We'll
have this under control...

51:39.920 --> 51:41.604
Ladies and gentlemen!

51:41.760 --> 51:46.402
I give you the next
Indy 500 champion!

51:46.840 --> 51:48.330
Huh? Huh?

51:48.800 --> 51:51.770
Is that a snail?

51:52.000 --> 51:55.447
Your driver is a snail?

52:02.440 --> 52:04.283
What kind of welcome is that?

52:04.440 --> 52:07.649
I'd say an appropriate
welcome, given the situation.

52:07.800 --> 52:09.245
All right.
Game over, nut job.

52:09.400 --> 52:10.599
Let's go.

52:10.600 --> 52:12.568
Have a nice flight, Chet.
Huh?

52:12.720 --> 52:14.290
Hit it!
White Shadow!

52:15.680 --> 52:17.011
