<i>Shelby Stone, hot
off her win in Sao Paulo.</i>

01:03:24.880 --> 01:03:27.929
<i>Oh, and there's Claudio Cruz, a.k.a.
"The Brazilian Butcher."</i>

01:03:28.080 --> 01:03:31.084
<i>He actually was a butcher before
